# React Component Patterns

## Component Structure
- **Use 'use client' directive** for client-side components
- **Import order**: React imports, then third-party, then local components
- **Export patterns**: Use named exports for components

## Navigation Components
- **Header**: [apps/web-app/src/components/layout/Header.tsx](mdc:apps/web-app/src/components/layout/Header.tsx)
